Geography information-t-bootstrap

bootstrapfunctiontest<-function(target.sample,n){
  temp=0
  for(i in 1:n){
    temp[i]=mean(target.sample[sample(1:length(target.sample),replace = TRUE)])
  }
  return (temp)
}
#Successful rate
